If hdr looks weird bright and green then type these in to console in this order:

Sv_cheats 1
mat_hdr_enabled 1(or enable cant remember)
buildcubemaps
mat_hdr_enabled 0(or enable cant remember)
buildcubemaps

Then reload map and everything should be fine.
